OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781269895
OL,3,CGuernsey could face 3% GST if plans
OL,4,Capproved
OL,6,FGuernsey's Policy and Resources
OL,7,FCommittee has proposed a 3% goods and
OL,8,Fservices tax (GST) as part of wider
OL,9,Freforms to plug the island's financial
OL,10,Fblack hole and support lower earners.
OL,12,FIf approved by the States, the changes
OL,13,Fcould come in from 2028.
OL,15,FThe proposed package includes some
OL,16,Fgood news, reducing the basic level of
OL,17,Fpersonal income tax to 15% for those
OL,18,Fwho make up to #28,000 a year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781269895
OL,3,CGuernsey could face 3% GST if plans
OL,4,Capproved
OL,6,FA 20% rate would be applied to all
OL,7,Fearnings above this threshold, while
OL,8,Fthe personal income tax allowance
OL,9,Fwould go up by #600.
OL,11,FAccording to the Committee, this would
OL,12,Fcost #28 million a year, but help
OL,13,Fthose on low and average incomes.
OL,15,FSocial security contributions would be
OL,16,Fadjusted under the proposed reforms,
OL,17,Fwith a new allowance of #11,122 for
OL,18,Femployed and self-employed people, and
OL,19,Fan increase in employer contributions
OL,20,Fto 7.6% by 2029.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781269895
OL,3,CGuernsey could face 3% GST if plans
OL,4,Capproved
OL,6,FWhen they pay social security, those
OL,7,Fwho are self-employed face a hike to
OL,8,F14.5%, while employees would see their
OL,9,Fcontributions climb to 8.5%.
OL,11,FThe rate that pensioners pay would
OL,12,Falso go up, to 4%.
OL,14,FThe Committee says its recommendations
OL,15,Fwould "improve public finances by an
OL,16,Festimated #59 million a year,
OL,17,Fincluding a minimum of #20 million of
OL,18,Fexpenditure reductions agreed by the
OL,19,FStates earlier this year and #39
OL,20,Fmillion in additional revenue from a
OL,21,Fblend of different sources".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781269895
OL,3,CGuernsey could face 3% GST if plans
OL,4,Capproved
OL,6,FIt adds: "The package is designed to
OL,7,Fhelp people on average and lower
OL,8,Fincomes ... while shifting the tax
OL,9,Fburden to those who can most afford
OL,10,Fit."
OL,12,FThere would also be a 25% drop in fuel
OL,13,Fduty, saving the average driver #130
OL,14,Fto #140 per year, and a new annual
OL,15,Fvehicle tax, also applied to electric
OL,16,Fand hybrid models, based on weight and
OL,17,Femissions. This would range from #25
OL,18,Fto #280.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781269895
OL,3,CGuernsey could face 3% GST if plans
OL,4,Capproved
OL,6,FAlso proposed in the package is an
OL,7,Fextension of the 10% corporate tax
OL,8,Frate to cover the entire profits of
OL,9,Fregulated businesses, and the
OL,10,FCommittee would consider extending
OL,11,Fthis to construction and retail firms
OL,12,Ffrom 2030.
OL,14,FDeputy Lindsay de Sausmarez, President
OL,15,Fof the Policy and Resources Committee,
OL,16,Fdescribed the package as "a balanced,
OL,17,Fpragmatic and proportionate response
OL,18,Fto the financial challenge we face".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781269895
OL,3,CGuernsey could face 3% GST if plans
OL,4,Capproved
OL,6,FShe said the tax reform proposals
OL,7,Fwould reduce Guernsey's "over-reliance
OL,8,Fon income-based taxation,
OL,9,Fstrengthening and diversifying our
OL,10,Fpublic finances in a way that raises
OL,11,Fmore income from a wider variety of
OL,12,Fsources whilst also reducing the tax
OL,13,Fburden on those that can least afford
OL,14,Fit".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781269895
OL,3,CGuernsey could face 3% GST if plans
OL,4,Capproved
OL,6,FThe Chief Minister added: "On the one
OL,7,Fhand, we urgently need to put our
OL,8,Fpublic finances on a stronger and more
OL,9,Fsustainable footing ... but at the
OL,10,Fsame time we're really, really
OL,11,Fconscious that many people in the
OL,12,Fcommunity are struggling to make ends
OL,13,Fmeet."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
